    • constant

      FieldBuilder<Self> constant(String name, Object value, Traversable<Mod> modifiers)
      Returns a builder for a compile-type constant field of this class. The modifiers Mod.STATIC and Mod.FINAL are added automatically and may be omitted. The value must be one of the types Boolean, Byte, Short, Integer, Long, Float, Double, Character or String. The type of the field is determined by the value. Type annotations may be put on the field type by typeAnnotation() method.
      Parameters:
      name - the field name.
      value - the value of this constant.
      modifiers - field modifiers among Mod.DEPRECATED, Mod.PRIVATE, Mod.PROTECTED, Mod.PUBLIC, Mod.SYNTHETIC, Mod.TRANSIENT and Mod.VOLATILE.

    • constant

      default FieldBuilder<Self> constant(String name, Object value, Mod... modifiers)

The value must be one of the types Boolean, Byte, Short, Integer, Long, Float, Double, Character or String. The type of the field is determined by the value.
